was provided by 
<bibRefCitation author="Ferrell, C. S. &amp; D. E. Wilson" bookContentInfo="5 pp." journalOrPublisher="Mamm. Species 373" pageId="119" pageNumber="119" refId="ref93021" refString="Ferrell, C. S., and D. E. Wilson 1991. Platyrrhinus helleri. Mamm. Species 373: 5 pp." title="Platyrrhinus helleri" type="book" year="1991">Ferrell and Wilson (1991)</bibRefCitation>
