(see also 
<bibRefCitation author="Rouk, C. S. &amp; D. C. Carter" bookContentInfo="7 pp." box="[128,422,1388,1411]" journalOrPublisher="Occas. Pap. Mus. Texas Tech Univ" pageId="119" pageNumber="119" refId="ref99776" refString="Rouk, C. S., and D. C. Carter 1972. A new species of Vampyrops (Chiroptera: Phyllostomatidae) from South America. Occas. Pap. Mus. Texas Tech Univ. 1: 7 pp." title="A new species of Vampyrops (Chiroptera: Phyllostomatidae) from South America" type="book" year="1972">Rouk and Carter, 1972</bibRefCitation>
